text: Sanbor Shullai is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Meghalaya Legislative Assembly from South Shillong as a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. ==References== Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Meghalaya Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Members of the Meghalaya Legislative Assembly Category:People from Shillong Category:Meghalaya MLAs 2018– Category:Nationalist Congress Party politicians from Meghalaya
title: Sanbor Shullai
